.hasClass(className)
检查元素是否包含某个class，返回true/false
Determine whether any of the matched elements are assigned the given class.
$( "#mydiv" ).hasClass( "foo" )
.toggleClass(className)
toggle是切换的意思，方法用于切换，switch是个bool类型值，这个看例子就明白
Some text.
